data.description: Gorgeous, turn-key, corner lot 3 bed 2.5 bath home nestled in an established, quiet subdivision just minutes from I-49 and Lafayette! This home has a sizeable master bedroom with tray ceilings and a large bathroom with an even larger walk-in closet. The split floor plan has the other 2 bedrooms on the opposite side of the home. The back patio already has a faucet and sink and is ready for the rest of the outdoor kitchen. No flood zone and no flooding ever. Refrigerator stays.
